thread.title: SA jobless rate still high

title: SA jobless rate still high
text:
Thu, Sep 10, 2015, 1:09 PM AEST - Australia Markets close in 2 hrs 51 mins SA jobless rate still high AAP – 9 minutes ago Print 
South Australia continues to have the worst jobless rate in the country but the state government says it takes "some comfort" from the latest figures. 
Unemployment in SA remained stable at 7.9 per cent in August despite the national rate dipping to 6.2 per cent. 
Employment Minister Gail Gago says there's still much work for the government to do but she takes some comfort from the fact that employment has been growing for the past eight months. @y7finance on Twitter, become a fan on Facebook Cabbies march on NSW parliament AAP
